  • Gopal Sharma 1. Any cash deposited more than 2 lacS in a year or 50 thousand in one slip must be informed to IT
    : So till March 2017 whatever money deposited will be viewed by IT after July 2017 ie after return.
    If cash is not matching to return, this deposit ca    n be added to return after questioning .
    Final tax will be calculated and demand for additional tax will be raised
    So don't deposit more than 49 thousand in one day and total deposit should not exceed 25% of total income.

    I am not expert so just giving my opinion.
